%h2 Bid for an Activity

%p These are the activities you can bid for. You need to tell us whether you will be attending or not. To do this, click on the activity, read the details and follow the instructions.

%table.eventlist{ :cellspacing => 0 }
  %thead
    %tr
      %th Activity
      %th Date
  %tbody
    - @future_events.each do |event|
      %tr
        %td
          %a{:href => "/events/#{event.id}"} #{event.truncated_title}
        %td #{event.date}
  

        
      